Change Log:

  24 March 2008 - Cleaned up package installation. It no longer
	          installs SickConfig.hh or the utility headers.
		  Credit to Tully Foote for the suggestion. -JCD

  30 June  2010 - Applied patch to include stdlib.h in examples.
	          This corrects issues compiling with gcc 4.3 and
		  newer. Credit to Morgan Quigley and Blaise
		  Gassend for this patch. -JCD  

		  Applied patch to fix bug in SickException.h that
		  may return an invalid const char* pointer. Credit
		  to Philipp Aumayr and Simon Opelt for this patch.
		  -JCD
		  
